Example of visualizing dense values

steps = 0:5:50
steps = 0:5:1000
steps = [50, 1000]
end_of_injection = findfirst(isequal(50), steps)
@assert !isnothing(end_of_injection)
end_of_migration = findfirst(isequal(1000), steps)
@assert !isnothing(end_of_migration)
